## Row {data-height="500"}

### Mapas de número de becados por provincia entre 2019 - 2022


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
gg_01 <- ggplot(n_prov) +
  theme_map(base_size = 18) +
  geom_sf(aes(fill = n), color = "gray90", size = 0.05) +
  facet_wrap(~ ano, ncol = 4) +
  geom_sf_label(aes(label = n), label.padding = unit(0.1, "lines"), size = 3) +
  scale_fill_viridis_c(name = "Número de becados", option = "C") +
  theme(legend.position = "bottom",
        strip.background = element_blank()) +
  theme(legend.key.height = unit(0.4, "cm"),
        legend.key.width = unit(2, "cm")) +
  guides(fill = guide_colourbar(label.theme = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1)))
gg_01
```

::: {.cell-output-display}
![](becas_una_files/figure-html/unnamed-chunk-20-1.png){width=2304}
:::
:::
